external_knowledge:
- 'Most active users' refers to users with the highest total activity (posts + replies); 
- 'Total contributions' means the sum of posts and replies; 
- 'Total likes' refers to the sum of likes received from all posts and replies; 
- Ranking is done based on total activity in descending order, then by total likes in descending order.

sql:
SELECT tag_name, usage_count
FROM tags
ORDER BY usage_count DESC;

SELECT user_id, session_duration
FROM user_sessions
ORDER BY session_duration DESC;
